# Cloud Computing Technology (2110524)

## Course Overview
**Course Code:** 2110524  
**Credits:** 3 units  
**Department:** Computer Engineering, Faculty of Engineering  
**Semester:** Spring 2025 (Academic Year 2568)  
**Instructor:** Asst. Prof. Dr. Kulwadee Sripanidkulchai (Sections 21, 1, 5)

### Prerequisites
- Operating Systems
- Computer Networks

### Course Description
This course covers cloud computing technologies, including the front-end and back-end operations of cloud systems, and the appropriate application and selection of cloud solutions for different system requirements.

## Assessment Breakdown
- **Activity/Homework:** 40%
- **Midterm Project:** 20%
- **Final Project:** 30%
- **Certification Preparation Assessment:** 10%

